IntProperty1Hint: The ID of the textbox used in the mes_color_bin file. First ID is 0!
IntProperty2Hint: A value of 0 is just idling, a value of 1 is walking
IntProperty3Hint: Determines various costume combos Chicks use. From pigtails, to bowties, to dress, to hat. Up to 15 combos used
IntProperty4Hint: Color for costumes. 0 is Red, 1 Green, 2 Blue, 3 Magenta, 4 Cyan, 5 Orange
FloatProperty2Hint: Add/Subtracts the default 50 units. Requires Movement type to be 1
FloatProperty3Hint: Add/Subtracts the default 0.6 units/frame speed. **Subtracting more than 0.49 crashes the game**
